        {
            "title": "美國原油出口量料創紀錄 全球供應吃緊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Kpler, vessel tracking, shipping report, US Customs data compiled by Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"615\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HYc.R42LzFxrJulgablX_g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/085780cc77c8fa66b18cb975b0e9e921\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Kpler, vessel tracking, shipping report, US Customs data compiled by Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國墨西哥灣沿岸原油日出口量5月料創紀錄，達到500萬桶，因亞洲買家大量採購以彌補中東供應的減少。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據當前裝船情況，4月原油日出口量已逐步接近約490萬桶，高於3月的約397萬桶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著越來越多的超大型油輪（VLCC）在墨西哥灣沿岸裝運，分析師目前預計，5月原油出口量將進一步上升。「美國原油出口看起來將延續我們在4月看到的強勁勢頭，」Kpler大宗商品研究主管Matt Smith表示。他補充稱，隨著亞洲需求保持高位，5月日出口量可能突破500萬桶大關 —— 超過此前450萬桶的紀錄。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-86be8417-14ac-3ca0-9b2c-a54bbfc52e54-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著夏季需求高峰臨近，如果出口持續激增，美國煉油商將不得不支付更高價格以將原油留在國內。汽油價格已升至2022年以來最高水平，超過每加侖4美元，如果汽油價格進一步上漲，可能在即將到來的中期選舉中給川普所屬的共和黨帶來政治風險。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"615\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FQFLSg1WISLtIpHWZiRU_Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e467e7f58488fa8844c6f916d76787ea\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Oil Exports to Hit 5 Million Barrels a Day Amid Global Crunch</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Charles Gorrivan.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E9%87%8F%E6%96%99%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%90%83%E7%B7%8A-172504636.html",
